@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram - Microwave Oven

[*] --> Idle

state "Idle" as Idle
Idle : entry / Display current time
Idle : do / Wait for user input

Idle --> WaitingForInput : [User selects power level or enters cooking time]

state "Waiting for input" as WaitingForInput
WaitingForInput : entry / Display power level options
WaitingForInput : do / Get user input
WaitingForInput : exit / Start cooking or cancel

WaitingForInput --> Cooking : [User selects power level and enters cooking time]
WaitingForInput --> Cancel : [User cancels cooking process]

state "Cooking" as Cooking
Cooking : entry / Start cooking process
Cooking : do / Monitor cooking time
Cooking : exit / Cooking complete or door opened

Idle --> DoorOpened : [Door is open during operation]
DoorOpened --> Idle : [Door closed during operation]

Cooking --> Stopped : [Cooking complete]
Stopped --> Idle : [User stops cooking process]

Cooking --> DoorOpened : [Door opened during cooking]
DoorOpened --> Idle : [Door closed during cooking]

state "Cancel" as Cancel
Cancel : entry / Cancel cooking process
Cancel --> Idle : [User cancels cooking process]

state "Door opened" as DoorOpened
DoorOpened --> Idle : [Door closed during operation]

state "Stopped" as Stopped
Stopped --> Idle : [User stops or cancels cooking process]

state End <<choice>>
Idle --> End : [System is idle]
WaitingForInput --> End : [User input is received]
Cooking --> End : [Cooking process is complete or interrupted]
DoorOpened --> End : [Door is opened during cooking process]
Cancel --> End : [Cooking process is cancelled]

@enduml
